{"tid":910589,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[水為財] 高鐵西九龍總站又漏水　B2層再現「水塘」","createTime":"2018-11-21T09:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T18:33:19.000Z","uid":23707,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ec74077ff4909388dc7a996111c97b216275610e","tid":910589,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:39:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181121/bkn-20181121171233244-1121_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181121%2Fbkn-20181121171233244-1121_00822_001.html&d=RX7ZHns07AflqApY6FlLge9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=80b7618c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181121/bkn-20181121171233244-1121_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n曾被揭發漏水的高鐵西九龍總站，繼本月1日有消防花灑啟動，令B2等多個樓層變水塘後，至今午（21日）4時許，有《東網》讀者發現上址B2層的天花又漏水，大量水如下雨般淋至地面，致該層又成水塘。記者於下午5時許到場視察，發現已經停止漏水，惟地上有大量積水，受影響範圍約30乘15米，部分商戶需暫時拉閘，停止營業，有職員在場清理積水。現場所見，今次漏水的位置與上次事發的Food Court相距不遠。<br />\n<br />\n本月1日下午2時許，一輛外來貨車駛經車站B1樓層停車場，撞毀一組消防花灑，同時，職員留意到車站1樓近N出口附近，有一組消防花灑啟動，控制室職員亦見到消防系統燈號亮起，於是派員到場了解，確定沒有火警後，即關上涉事花灑頭，並立即安排工程人員檢查。而部分水流到對下的B1、B2樓層相近位置，令多層天花有水不停滴下，儼如落雨般。"},{"pid":"e4a283641debd1a92a664ee96df7182ec30c70d9","tid":910589,"uid":33307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:40:17.000Z","msg":"高鐵唔興啦，依家講列根號呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076ee66c0a02fe94d899ec2a9ae11aff648f0068","tid":910589,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615d137d31666a194c55bf4ef0cf2fe0377b0741","tid":910589,"uid":80416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:54:43.000Z","msg":"已經無人理高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4345ed2f5e47a73dc294cb4b9430fe346ec1f2aa","tid":910589,"uid":175667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T18:27:30.000Z","msg":"落雨漏水好出奇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202160a9cf947549e9e2e9410122fc337af38f89","tid":910589,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T18:33:19.000Z","msg":"安樂都走數啦"}]}